(amended after 
<bibRefCitation box="[763,1058,1291,1317]" pageId="4" pageNumber="326" refId="ref8658" refString="Bergquist, P. R. &amp; Cook, S. D. C. (2002) Order Verongida Bergquist, 1978. In: Hooper, J. N. A. &amp; Van Soest, R. W. M. (Eds.), Systema Porifera: A guide to the classification of sponges. Fol. I. Kluwer Academic / Plenum Publishers, New York, Boston, Dordrecht, London and Moscow, pp. 1081 - 1096. https: // doi. org / 10.1007 / 978 - 1 - 4615 - 0747 - 5 _ 108" type="book chapter">Bergquist &amp; Cook 2002</bibRefCitation>
